        "id": "sample_1",
        "input": "1\n2 2 2",
        "output": "6",
        "explanation": "Explanation:\nF(2⋅1,2⋅1)=F(2,2)=3F(2 \\cdot 1, 2 \\cdot 1) = F(2, 2) = 3F(2⋅1,2⋅1)=F(2,2)=3.\nF(2⋅2,2⋅2)=F(4,4)=3F(2 \\cdot 2, 2 \\cdot 2) = F(4, 4) = 3F(2⋅2,2⋅2)=F(4,4)=3.\n\nThus, the answer is 3+3=63 + 3 = 63+3=6."
